==Description==
The '''Flame Plate''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Flame Plate''' has a value of 100 [[Gems|Fire Gems]] {{Gem|Fire}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Acquisition==
Flame Plates can be found in the [[Underground]] and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

